Introduction

SCSI - Small Computer Systems Interface

protocol to access various I/O devices
disks, CD-ROMs, tape drives, scanners...

various physical interfaces
parallel SCSI, SAS, FiberChannel, IEEE-1394, USB

software emulation
SATA and RAID controllers in OpenBSD

